⍝ ZBus.Nats Object Store + Services test
⍝ Validates: obj store create/put/get/del, service create + endpoint
⍝ Requires nats-server -js running on localhost:4222

⎕IO ⎕ML←1
pass←1
tests←0 ⋄ passed←0

dll←'D:\devel\Z-Format\src\ZBus.Nats\bin\Release\net10.0\win-x64\publish\ZBus.Nats.dll'

⍝ ── Define ⎕NA bindings ──────────────────────────────────────────────

'zbus_init'         ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_init <0T1 >Z'
'zbus_wait'         ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_wait& <0T1 I4 >Z >Z >Z'
'zbus_close'        ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_close <0T1'
'zbus_describe'     ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_describe <0T1 >Z'
'nats_connect'      ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_connect <0T1 <0T1'
'nats_pub'          ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_pub <0T1 <0T1 <Z'
'nats_obj'          ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_obj <0T1 =Z'
'nats_obj_get'      ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_obj_get <0T1 <0T1 >Z'
'nats_obj_put'      ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_obj_put <0T1 <0T1 <Z'
'nats_obj_del'      ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_obj_del <0T1 <0T1'
'nats_service'      ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_service <0T1 <0T1 =Z'
'nats_endpoint'     ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_endpoint <0T1 <0T1 <0T1'
'nats_request'      ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_request <0T1 <0T1 <0T1 I4 =Z'

⎕←'══════════════════════════════════════════'
⎕←' ZBus.Nats Object Store + Services Tests'
⎕←'══════════════════════════════════════════'
⎕←''

⍝ ── Setup ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

(rc rn)←zbus_init 'OS' 0
rc←nats_connect 'OS' 'nats://localhost:4222'
(rc obj evt data)←zbus_wait 'OS' 5000 0 0 0
:If evt≢'Connected' ⋄ ⎕←'FATAL: not connected' ⋄ ⎕OFF 1 ⋄ :EndIf
⎕←'Connected to NATS'
⎕←''

⍝ ═══════════════════════════════════════════
⍝ Object Store tests
⍝ ═══════════════════════════════════════════

⎕←'Test 1: Create object store'
(rc storeName)←nats_obj 'OS' 'blobs'
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ store created: ',storeName
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ create failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 2: Put object'
rc←nats_obj_put storeName 'hello.txt' 'Hello, Object Store!'
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ put hello.txt'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ put failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 3: Get object'
(rc data)←nats_obj_get storeName 'hello.txt' 0
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    ⎕←'  bytes: ',⍕data
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ got hello.txt (',(⍕≢data),' bytes)'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ get failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 4: Delete object'
rc←nats_obj_del storeName 'hello.txt'
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ deleted hello.txt'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ delete failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⍝ ═══════════════════════════════════════════
⍝ Services tests
⍝ ═══════════════════════════════════════════

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 5: Create service'
(rc svcName)←nats_service 'OS' 'echo' ('Echo service' '1.0.0')
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ service created: ',svcName
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ service creation failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 6: Add endpoint'
rc←nats_endpoint svcName 'ping' 'echo.ping'
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ endpoint added: echo.ping'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ endpoint add failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 7: Request to service endpoint'
⍝ Send request to the service endpoint
(rc reqName)←nats_request 'OS' 'R1' 'echo.ping' 3000 'ping!'
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ request sent to echo.ping'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ request failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⍝ Service should receive the Request event
(rc obj evt data)←zbus_wait 'OS' 3000 0 0 0
tests+←1
:If evt≡'Request'
    msgSubj←1⊃data
    replyTo←2⊃data
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ service received Request on ',msgSubj
    ⍝ Reply back
    rc←nats_pub 'OS' replyTo 'pong!'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ expected Request event, got ',evt,' on ',obj
:EndIf

⍝ Requester should get Reply
(rc obj evt data)←zbus_wait 'OS' 3000 0 0 0
tests+←1
:If evt≡'Reply'
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ requester got Reply'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ expected Reply, got ',evt
:EndIf

⍝ ── Describe ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 10: Describe service'
(rc info)←zbus_describe svcName 0
tests+←1
:If (rc=0)∧((2⊃info)≡'Service')
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ type=Service'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ describe: rc=',(⍕rc)
:EndIf

⍝ ── Cleanup ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
rc←zbus_close ⊂'OS'

⎕←'══════════════════════════════════════════'
⎕←' Results: ',(⍕passed),'/',(⍕tests),' passed'
:If pass
    ⎕←' ═══ ALL OBJ/SVC TESTS PASSED ═══'
:Else
    ⎕←' *** SOME TESTS FAILED ***'
:EndIf
⎕←'══════════════════════════════════════════'
